{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.120", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.040", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.880", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "16\u00a0Jahre f\u00fchrt die NATO jetzt in Afghanistan Krieg\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.480", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit deutscher Beteiligung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "George Bush rief 2001 mit seinen B\u00fcndnispartnern global den sogenannten Krieg gegen den Terror aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dem sich seitdem alle Bundesregierungen beteiligt haben; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens h\u00e4tte auch eine m\u00f6gliche Jamaika-Koalition diesen Krieg fortgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.160", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch damit h\u00e4tten wir keine gro\u00dfe \u00c4nderung dieser Politik hier erlebt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.720", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut einer Studie der \u00c4rzteorganisation IPPNW sind allein in Afghanistan mindestens 220\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen get\u00f6tet worden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Pakistan 80\u00a0000, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.160", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und im Irak sind \u00fcber 1\u00a0Million Menschen direkt get\u00f6tet worden oder an den Kriegsfolgen gestorben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.280", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser globale Krieg der NATO bedeutet Terror f\u00fcr Millionen Menschen und z\u00fcchtet immer nur neuen Terror. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Welt ist nicht sicherer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern unsicherer geworden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zeigen auch mehr und mehr die Terrorangriffe in den westlichen Metropolen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.000", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke hat sich immer gegen diesen globalen Krieg gestemmt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.920", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das werden wir auch weiterhin tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Afghanistan hei\u00dft das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass \u00fcber 2,5\u00a0Millionen Menschen ins Ausland geflohen sind und 1,2\u00a0Millionen Menschen im Land auf der Flucht sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Afghanistan z\u00e4hlt weiterhin zu den \u00e4rmsten L\u00e4ndern der Erde und hat eine der korruptesten Regierungen der Welt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.080", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Sicherheitslage ist besorgniserregend."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau von der Leyen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Ihrer M\u00e4rchenstunde hier\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss ich wirklich sagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr ein Bild von Afghanistan gezeichnet haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.960", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist wirklich skandal\u00f6s."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das deutsche Generalkonsulat ist geschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die deutsche Botschaft ist nach einem schweren Anschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.440", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei dem mehr als 160\u00a0Menschen get\u00f6tet wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.600", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenfalls geschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.640", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vereinten Nationen haben allein in diesem Jahr offiziell \u00fcber 8\u00a0000 Zivilisten registriert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die entweder get\u00f6tet oder verwundet wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All diese Zahlen zeigen doch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die NATO hat in Afghanistan nichts verloren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.440", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie muss abziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen will sie jetzt den Krieg versch\u00e4rft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.480", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie von US-Pr\u00e4sident Donald Trump angeordnet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.000", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weiterf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.640", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen Abzugstermin gibt es nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.160", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die USA sagen selbst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihre neue Afghanistan-Strategie lautet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.720", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr Luftangriffe und verdeckte Operationen f\u00fcr den Vers\u00f6hnungsprozess. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.160", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen die Taliban nach eigenen Aussagen an den Verhandlungstisch bomben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.880", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist das eine politische L\u00f6sung f\u00fcr Afghanistan? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da kann ich nur den Kopf sch\u00fctteln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.760", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern stattdessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.600", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundeswehr sich an dieser versch\u00e4rften Kriegsf\u00fchrung nicht beteiligt und dass sie vollst\u00e4ndig aus Afghanistan abgezogen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen ebenfalls, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die US-Drohnenmorde in Afghanistan zur Versch\u00e4rfung der Situation beitragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.160", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie viel Hass sch\u00fcren und dazu f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.280", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Taliban immer mehr neue K\u00e4mpfer rekrutieren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Drohnenkrieg wird unter anderem auch von der US-Air-Base Ramstein gef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.520", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcberwacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gesteuert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.960", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt auch f\u00fcr AFRICOM Stuttgart. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit sich die Bundesregierung nicht weiter der Beihilfe f\u00fcr extralegale T\u00f6tungen schuldig macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.800", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wollen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Air Base Ramstein und das Hauptquartier von AFRICOM geschlossen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.240", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders heuchlerisch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss ich sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist Ihre Argumentation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.720", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau von der Leyen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundeswehr zur Stabilit\u00e4t und Sicherheit in Afghanistan beitragen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.440", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "womit der afghanischen Zivilbev\u00f6lkerung vor Ort geholfen w\u00fcrde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn aber afghanische Fl\u00fcchtlinge hierherkommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann wird ihnen nicht geholfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann werden sie abgeschoben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine R\u00fcckkehr nach Afghanistan kann aber den Tod bedeuten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine menschenverachtende und skandal\u00f6se Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.080", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Abschiebungen gestoppt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.920", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie selbst k\u00f6nnen auch gar nicht folgerichtig argumentieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einerseits sagen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundeswehr deshalb in dieses Land geschickt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.240", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Sicherheitslage dort so gef\u00e4hrlich und instabil ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.080", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Andererseits schicken Sie Menschen und Familien in dieses Land zur\u00fcck. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.360", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier zeigen Sie offene Widerspr\u00fcche. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.440", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine solche Politik ist wirklich verwerflich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.720", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "skandal\u00f6s und unmenschlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.840", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden das nicht unterst\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.320", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir setzen uns daf\u00fcr ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.120", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Abschiebungen gestoppt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.960", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner ist J\u00fcrgen Trittin f\u00fcr die Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
 ]
}